WEBVTT

00:00:11.105 --> 00:00:12.065
{\an8}Watch out!

00:00:13.865 --> 00:00:15.065
{\an8}Oh, no!

00:00:15.145 --> 00:00:16.025
{\an8}What’s wrong?

00:00:16.105 --> 00:00:17.825
{\an8}My… My necklace is gone!

00:00:17.905 --> 00:00:20.505
{\an8}-Did the person who hit you take it?
-Wait!

00:00:20.585 --> 00:00:22.345
{\an8}You thief! Give it back!

00:00:22.425 --> 00:00:24.705
{\an8}I’m returning it to you, and that’s it.

00:00:25.665 --> 00:00:29.105
{\an8}Why was it okay when he touched my hand?

00:00:30.505 --> 00:00:32.625
{\an8}-Damn it!
-Ouch! Who did this?

00:00:34.865 --> 00:00:36.585
{\an8}-You started it.
-You want a piece of me?

00:00:36.665 --> 00:00:38.305
{\an8}What if I do?

00:01:49.105 --> 00:01:52.185
Mom, when did we hire this baker?

00:01:52.985 --> 00:01:54.865
When was the tasting?
How come I wasn't told?

00:01:55.505 --> 00:01:59.385
You weren't here when
he came for the tasting yesterday.

00:01:59.465 --> 00:02:02.025
His desserts are amazing.

00:02:02.105 --> 00:02:04.905
He even has experience
from a Thai dessert shop.

00:02:04.985 --> 00:02:07.905
Pi Tawan, his desserts are to die for.

00:02:07.985 --> 00:02:09.345
You’ve got to try.

00:02:16.545 --> 00:02:17.545
No thanks.

00:02:18.105 --> 00:02:19.225
Your loss.

00:02:20.625 --> 00:02:22.505
Suit yourself.

00:02:22.585 --> 00:02:24.345
-DinDin, let’s get to work.
-Yes.

00:02:25.345 --> 00:02:26.345
You got it.

00:02:32.265 --> 00:02:35.265
Something going on… between you two?

00:02:36.265 --> 00:02:37.145
-Nothing!
-No!

00:02:37.225 --> 00:02:38.705
Ooh, suspicious…

00:03:01.945 --> 00:03:03.345
Don’t think I’ve
forgotten about that night.

00:03:25.025 --> 00:03:27.865
Not my fault. I tried to
wake you, but you wouldn’t budge.

00:03:31.025 --> 00:03:32.305
Are you a "hit and run" guy?

00:03:33.865 --> 00:03:36.185
It was just
a "friends with benefits" thing.

00:03:36.785 --> 00:03:37.625
Haven't you heard of it?

00:03:39.265 --> 00:03:40.465
But you left me there alone,

00:03:41.345 --> 00:03:42.665
completely naked.

00:03:44.025 --> 00:03:46.225
You wouldn’t wake up.

00:03:46.825 --> 00:03:48.905
I even covered you with your clothes.

00:03:49.545 --> 00:03:52.825
The wind must’ve blown
them away. I had to get to work.

00:03:53.425 --> 00:03:56.065
Unlike you, I actually have a job to do.

00:03:56.145 --> 00:04:00.865
-Are you trying to piss me off?
-I’m not. You’re the one nagging me.

00:04:00.945 --> 00:04:02.465
Do you want these croissants or not?

00:04:04.225 --> 00:04:09.505
We’ve got a rush order!
Ten boxes of eclairs for a regular, ASAP!

00:04:09.585 --> 00:04:11.625
Right now? I’m making croissants.

00:04:11.705 --> 00:04:14.105
It’ll have to wait. Baking takes time.

00:04:14.185 --> 00:04:15.465
Please?

00:04:16.345 --> 00:04:19.225
Come on… Please, please, please?

00:04:21.624 --> 00:04:23.265
Fine. I’ll get right on it.

00:04:23.345 --> 00:04:24.985
Thanks!

00:04:30.865 --> 00:04:34.105
Why are you still here, old man?
You’re in my way.

00:04:34.985 --> 00:04:37.265
Just do your job. I’m staying right here.

00:04:39.065 --> 00:04:40.985
-Nothing better to do?
-I do now.

00:04:42.145 --> 00:04:45.705
I don’t trust you.
Who knows what you might steal from here.

00:04:46.505 --> 00:04:47.425
You’re nuts.

00:05:32.345 --> 00:05:35.545
Hello. Do you have an appointment?

00:05:36.505 --> 00:05:38.345
Ah, no… I don’t.

00:05:39.505 --> 00:05:41.905
I’m actually here to see Dr. Nabnueng.

00:05:41.985 --> 00:05:47.425
Oh, he’s out for field work today.

00:05:47.505 --> 00:05:48.865
Field work?

00:05:48.945 --> 00:05:52.505
Yes, our doctors take turns going out

00:05:52.585 --> 00:05:56.545
to support those
at risk of mental health issues.

00:05:56.625 --> 00:06:01.625
Including the homeless,
nightlife workers, and those…

00:06:01.705 --> 00:06:04.265
with limited access to care.

00:06:07.385 --> 00:06:08.585
Interesting.

00:06:10.625 --> 00:06:14.105
May I ask if you are one of his patients?

00:06:14.825 --> 00:06:15.945
N-no… not really.

00:06:18.105 --> 00:06:21.145
Actually, yes. I just became one.

00:06:25.345 --> 00:06:29.065
Do you happen to know where he is today?

00:06:30.905 --> 00:06:32.145
Yes, I do.

00:06:36.825 --> 00:06:39.865
Doctor, I’m so scared.

00:06:40.705 --> 00:06:44.945
There’s no legal protection
for people like us.

00:06:45.025 --> 00:06:47.585
Only criminal laws that punish us.

00:06:47.665 --> 00:06:52.705
The recent events have left us terrified.

00:06:52.785 --> 00:06:56.425
I don’t know where to turn or what to do.

00:06:58.105 --> 00:06:59.265
I hear you.

00:07:00.145 --> 00:07:03.705
What you've been through…
must be traumatizing.

00:07:03.785 --> 00:07:05.385
Yes.

00:07:05.465 --> 00:07:11.985
But it’s worse when we’re alone.
With no way out, we feel more depressed.

00:07:13.705 --> 00:07:15.985
What makes you feel
that way at those times?

00:07:16.985 --> 00:07:18.785
Maybe we're just exhausted from work.

00:07:19.425 --> 00:07:22.825
Society, the economy, the unstable income.

00:07:23.345 --> 00:07:25.785
No one will hire us for any other job.

00:07:26.345 --> 00:07:28.105
I’m at a dead end, Doctor.

00:07:29.425 --> 00:07:30.625
I understand.

00:07:31.305 --> 00:07:32.705
You have every right to feel exhausted.

00:07:32.785 --> 00:07:34.545
Everyone here…

00:07:34.625 --> 00:07:36.705
has the right to feel
whatever you’re feeling.

00:07:37.305 --> 00:07:40.945
But the most important thing is,

00:07:41.025 --> 00:07:42.225
please don’t carry it all alone.

00:07:42.985 --> 00:07:47.545
Reach out to those around you.
Friends, or even me.

00:07:47.625 --> 00:07:51.505
Talk about it. Share your burdens with us.

00:07:52.105 --> 00:07:54.265
We’ll find a way through this together.

00:07:56.985 --> 00:07:58.745
If anyone has something

00:07:58.825 --> 00:08:04.465
too personal for a group setting,

00:08:04.545 --> 00:08:05.785
you're welcome to speak with me privately.

00:08:06.785 --> 00:08:07.865
Thank you.

00:08:32.705 --> 00:08:33.545
Sailom?

00:08:36.385 --> 00:08:37.585
What brings you here?

00:08:38.144 --> 00:08:43.024
Oh… I was just passing by.

00:08:44.865 --> 00:08:48.065
What about you? What are you doing here?

00:08:49.985 --> 00:08:52.265
It’s field work with the SWING Foundation.

00:08:52.785 --> 00:08:55.305
Providing counseling
for nightlife workers.

00:08:55.385 --> 00:08:58.345
They deserve the same
protections as everyone else.

00:08:59.305 --> 00:09:00.585
I see.

00:09:01.225 --> 00:09:04.465
I thought you only saw patients
at the clinic.

00:09:04.545 --> 00:09:06.025
I didn't expect to see you out here.

00:09:06.865 --> 00:09:08.705
I just want to help out however I can.

00:09:13.985 --> 00:09:14.825
Are you hungry?

00:09:15.865 --> 00:09:16.705
Huh?

00:09:17.425 --> 00:09:18.265
Hungry for what?

00:09:18.865 --> 00:09:21.625
Hungry for dinner. Want to go grab a bite?

00:09:42.105 --> 00:09:43.585
Still not done?

00:09:44.385 --> 00:09:45.385
Not even close.

00:09:45.465 --> 00:09:48.625
They're bickering like crazy in there.
The filling is taking forever.

00:09:48.705 --> 00:09:49.745
What are they fighting about?

00:09:50.385 --> 00:09:53.105
Pi Tawan’s been hovering
in the kitchen all day.

00:09:53.185 --> 00:09:57.545
They've been at it for an hour.
So many éclairs wasted.

00:09:59.185 --> 00:10:01.745
Are we gonna make it in time?

00:10:03.585 --> 00:10:05.985
No clue. See for yourself.

00:10:07.105 --> 00:10:09.705
Nah, Pi Tawan will just yell at me.

00:10:09.785 --> 00:10:13.505
So… what now?

00:10:22.105 --> 00:10:23.065
How much longer are you gonna stare?

00:10:27.105 --> 00:10:28.305
Damn it…

00:10:30.705 --> 00:10:33.465
Look! It's ruined
because you keep staring.

00:10:33.545 --> 00:10:34.865
It’s all messy now.

00:10:35.385 --> 00:10:36.865
How can I finish them on time?

00:10:41.345 --> 00:10:44.545
Seriously,
have you ever even baked before?

00:10:46.705 --> 00:10:48.305
I don’t think you have.

00:10:51.145 --> 00:10:52.225
If you’re an expert,

00:10:53.305 --> 00:10:54.385
do it yourself.

00:10:57.145 --> 00:10:58.105
Me?

00:11:00.985 --> 00:11:05.025
If I could, why would my mom hire you?

00:11:11.385 --> 00:11:12.705
If you keep staring,

00:11:13.745 --> 00:11:14.745
I'm not doing it.

00:12:07.105 --> 00:12:09.145
How long since you returned to Thailand?

00:12:10.505 --> 00:12:13.105
About… seven years or so, I think?

00:12:14.985 --> 00:12:16.265
Why did you move to the US back then?

00:12:23.065 --> 00:12:23.985
Come and play with me.

00:12:24.745 --> 00:12:25.985
No, I don’t want to!

00:12:26.065 --> 00:12:27.785
-It’s just your dad!
-Let go!

00:12:27.865 --> 00:12:29.225
-No! Leave me alone!
-Come here!

00:12:29.825 --> 00:12:31.865
-I am your dad!
-Let me go!

00:12:31.945 --> 00:12:33.945
-I said, stay still!
-Let me go!

00:12:34.025 --> 00:12:36.585
Get over here! Now!

00:12:38.905 --> 00:12:42.225
I’m sorry. If it’s too personal,
you don’t have to tell me.

00:12:47.225 --> 00:12:49.585
Let’s eat. You must be starving by now.

00:12:51.065 --> 00:12:53.425
Order whatever you like.

00:12:54.265 --> 00:12:55.105
It's my treat.

00:12:56.785 --> 00:12:59.145
Excuse me. Menu, please?

00:13:06.505 --> 00:13:07.545
Can you eat this?

00:13:08.905 --> 00:13:10.025
Thank you.

00:13:20.625 --> 00:13:22.145
Honestly,

00:13:22.225 --> 00:13:26.105
it would be great
if sex work were fully decriminalized.

00:13:27.465 --> 00:13:32.385
The workers wouldn't have to
be victims like in tragic news stories.

00:13:32.985 --> 00:13:34.825
Yes, I agree.

00:13:36.705 --> 00:13:38.785
It would be much safer for them.

00:13:39.305 --> 00:13:42.185
They’d have welfare,
the state would get the tax,

00:13:44.185 --> 00:13:45.545
and they’d be protected
from being exploited.

00:13:46.425 --> 00:13:47.665
Most importantly,

00:13:48.345 --> 00:13:50.105
they wouldn't be lured and killed.

00:13:52.905 --> 00:13:54.025
It’s devastating.

00:13:57.585 --> 00:13:58.585
Let’s toast.

00:14:01.265 --> 00:14:02.545
No more heavy talk.

00:14:07.945 --> 00:14:08.905
Cheers!

00:14:16.065 --> 00:14:18.225
Whoa, easy!

00:14:18.985 --> 00:14:21.265
Take it slow, or you’ll get drunk.

00:14:22.945 --> 00:14:26.585
I’m fine, Doc. I can handle this much.

00:15:05.465 --> 00:15:06.985
"Not drunk at all," huh?

00:15:17.385 --> 00:15:21.785
Look who finally decided to show up.
I thought a customer had locked you away.

00:15:21.865 --> 00:15:23.305
No one can cage me, you know it.

00:15:24.225 --> 00:15:27.105
Can't be too sure. You're way too hot.

00:15:27.185 --> 00:15:30.985
Everyone was dying to see you yesterday.

00:15:31.625 --> 00:15:34.505
Especially the hottie
at that table over there.

00:15:47.105 --> 00:15:47.945
You mean Pi Man?

00:15:48.865 --> 00:15:50.385
That influencer from Suphanburi.

00:15:50.465 --> 00:15:55.025
Go charm him tonight.
He might drop a 500-drink bid on you.

00:15:55.545 --> 00:15:57.505
In your dreams.

00:15:57.585 --> 00:15:58.865
Just give it a shot.

00:16:00.865 --> 00:16:04.065
Welcome to The Loner Club.
We're here to cure your loneliness.

00:16:04.145 --> 00:16:08.065
Let the drink bidding begin!

00:16:08.145 --> 00:16:11.745
Okay, here’s Number 88 from Table V2.

00:16:11.825 --> 00:16:16.745
Ten drinks for Number 88 from
Table V2! Going once… going twice… SOLD!

00:16:16.825 --> 00:16:19.425
Ice, Number 88, you’re heading to V2!

00:16:20.585 --> 00:16:22.305
Any more bids?

00:16:23.105 --> 00:16:24.425
Number 69, 50 drinks!

00:16:24.505 --> 00:16:25.745
Ooh! 50 drinks for 69!

00:16:25.825 --> 00:16:30.865
Going once… twice… going--

00:16:30.945 --> 00:16:34.465
-100 drinks!
-100 drinks from Table 27!

00:16:34.545 --> 00:16:37.425
Going once… twice--

00:16:37.505 --> 00:16:39.705
-Make it 120!
-120 drinks!

00:16:39.785 --> 00:16:43.185
120 drinks. Going once… twice…

00:16:43.265 --> 00:16:45.345
and finally--

00:16:46.665 --> 00:16:48.065
200 drinks.

00:16:49.425 --> 00:16:54.425
200 drinks! Alright! Going once… twice…

00:16:54.505 --> 00:16:58.905
Sold! Table 17 takes the whole set!

00:16:58.985 --> 00:17:03.305
Sky is officially off
the floor tonight! Congratulations!

00:17:03.385 --> 00:17:05.305
Thank you so much, Sir, for…

00:17:15.865 --> 00:17:17.305
You’re hot.

00:17:22.265 --> 00:17:23.905
Number 28, 100 drinks!

00:17:23.985 --> 00:17:25.985
Number 28, 100 drinks!

00:17:26.065 --> 00:17:32.025
-Number 28. Going once… twice… SOLD!
-Yes.

00:17:32.105 --> 00:17:33.985
Off to Pi Man's table!

00:17:34.065 --> 00:17:36.945
He's off the floor as well!

00:17:37.025 --> 00:17:39.745
What are you drinking?
Want me to fix you a glass?

00:17:39.825 --> 00:17:43.305
Whiskey with soda, or just water?

00:17:43.385 --> 00:17:44.265
I…

00:17:44.345 --> 00:17:46.145
-Whiskey and water…
-Alright.

00:17:46.225 --> 00:17:48.705
Number eight?
How many drinks for Number eight?

00:17:48.785 --> 00:17:53.785
-Two drinks.
-Oh, two drinks from Table 27.

00:17:53.865 --> 00:17:59.225
Going once… twice… SOLD! To Table 27!

00:18:04.385 --> 00:18:05.545
Have some water first.

00:18:07.265 --> 00:18:08.985
You can really hold your liquor.

00:18:11.745 --> 00:18:16.545
This is my first time.
Didn’t know it would… feel this good.

00:18:16.625 --> 00:18:19.065
-Your first time drinking?
-Yup.

00:18:19.145 --> 00:18:21.185
-First time at a host club too?
-Mm-hmm.

00:18:22.105 --> 00:18:23.225
Do you like it?

00:18:25.305 --> 00:18:26.705
I do.

00:18:32.505 --> 00:18:35.465
So, what can you do besides mixing drinks?

00:18:36.185 --> 00:18:37.225
I can…

00:18:38.105 --> 00:18:40.545
play games, mix drinks…

00:18:40.625 --> 00:18:43.545
Basically, I can do whatever you want.

00:18:43.625 --> 00:18:44.865
Anything I want?

00:18:45.585 --> 00:18:47.425
Then… show me what you've got.

00:18:54.705 --> 00:18:56.705
Good boy. Here’s your reward.

00:19:00.625 --> 00:19:02.385
Easy there.

00:19:02.465 --> 00:19:03.945
You should have some water.

00:19:06.265 --> 00:19:09.105
Drink up. You'll feel better.

00:19:11.545 --> 00:19:12.385
You okay?

00:19:13.545 --> 00:19:16.665
The whiskey… it's gone. I need…

00:19:16.745 --> 00:19:19.465
Hey. Another bottle over here.

00:19:21.185 --> 00:19:24.465
-Let's stick with water for now.
-No. I want another bottle.

00:19:25.305 --> 00:19:26.265
Okay?

00:19:27.705 --> 00:19:29.425
-Please have some water first.
-Sure.

00:19:38.065 --> 00:19:38.985
You bastards!

00:19:39.985 --> 00:19:43.265
I’m just an old woman!
How can you be so heartless?!

00:19:43.345 --> 00:19:44.745
Shut up, old hag!

00:19:45.385 --> 00:19:47.425
It's your own fault
for not paying us back.

00:19:47.505 --> 00:19:50.345
If we could, we would've paid you by now!

00:19:50.425 --> 00:19:53.585
And why is the interest so damn high?!

00:19:53.665 --> 00:19:55.745
We pay so much,
but the debt never goes away!

00:19:56.345 --> 00:19:57.785
You've got a big mouth!

00:19:57.865 --> 00:19:58.825
Hey!

00:20:00.985 --> 00:20:02.505
Get your hands off my grandma!

00:20:05.905 --> 00:20:06.745
Are you okay?

00:20:08.545 --> 00:20:10.225
Like mother, like son.

00:20:11.385 --> 00:20:13.505
A deadbeat, just like your mom.

00:20:14.785 --> 00:20:17.665
No, DinDin! Please don’t!

00:20:17.745 --> 00:20:20.825
I was gonna give you more time.

00:20:20.905 --> 00:20:22.665
But on second thought,

00:20:23.425 --> 00:20:25.425
taking your house is much easier.

00:20:25.505 --> 00:20:28.185
You can't do that! We had a deal!

00:20:28.265 --> 00:20:30.385
But you've got nothing for my boss.

00:20:32.505 --> 00:20:33.505
I have it.

00:20:35.345 --> 00:20:36.625
I’ll transfer it right now.

00:20:44.505 --> 00:20:47.585
Three thousand?
That doesn’t even cover the interest!

00:20:49.945 --> 00:20:53.145
Just take it. That’s all I have.

00:20:56.185 --> 00:20:57.225
Let’s go.

00:20:58.705 --> 00:21:00.505
Better than nothing, I guess.

00:21:07.105 --> 00:21:08.385
Are you hurt, Grandma?

00:21:33.905 --> 00:21:35.465
Hey, is he that pilot?

00:21:37.385 --> 00:21:38.905
Which one?

00:21:38.985 --> 00:21:41.545
The one who botched
a landing and killed a kid.

00:21:44.265 --> 00:21:45.945
The guy from that viral TikTok?

00:21:46.865 --> 00:21:51.625
Oh, right. That girl was
the same age as my sister.

00:21:52.505 --> 00:21:56.065
Feel bad for her parents.
She was at such a sweet age.

00:21:56.145 --> 00:21:58.545
But she’s gone
because of one pathetic pilot.

00:22:00.225 --> 00:22:01.345
The hell you looking at?

00:22:02.065 --> 00:22:04.625
Oh, we got a tough guy here?

00:22:05.785 --> 00:22:08.105
You’re so thick-skinned!

00:22:08.185 --> 00:22:10.545
Killed a kid and still have
the nerve to sit here drinking!

00:22:10.625 --> 00:22:12.225
What the fuck is wrong with you people?!

00:22:18.665 --> 00:22:19.585
Take that!

00:23:34.985 --> 00:23:35.985
What the hell?

00:23:38.625 --> 00:23:39.705
What are you doing?

00:23:39.785 --> 00:23:41.265
Getting laid.

00:23:42.465 --> 00:23:44.465
I don’t sleep with just anyone.

00:23:53.425 --> 00:23:54.945
Just lie down next to me.

00:24:53.705 --> 00:24:54.985
Catch!

00:24:55.065 --> 00:24:56.145
Whoa!

00:25:24.105 --> 00:25:26.345
Pi Doc! Come play in the water with me!

00:25:26.865 --> 00:25:28.065
What? I can't hear you!

00:25:28.145 --> 00:25:29.665
Come on! Get in here!

00:25:30.305 --> 00:25:31.905
I don't have a change of clothes!

00:25:31.985 --> 00:25:33.065
Come on!

00:25:46.785 --> 00:25:48.585
He’s quite a dork when he's drunk.

00:25:50.785 --> 00:25:52.225
Come dance with me!

00:25:53.025 --> 00:25:54.625
-No! I don't know how to dance
-Now!

00:25:54.705 --> 00:25:56.145
Dance with me!

00:25:56.225 --> 00:25:57.905
I don’t know how!

00:25:57.985 --> 00:25:59.385
Then let me teach you!

